title: Bug 130068 [Regression] Report Parameter window doesn't pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
description:
Description: When previewing a report with parameters, the Report Parameter window does not pop up.
Steps to reproduce:
1. Open the report.
2. Click on the preview button.

Expected behavior: The Report Parameter window should pop up when previewing a report with parameters.

Actual behavior: The Report Parameter window is not popping up when previewing a report with parameters.
OB: The Report Parameter window does not pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
EB: The Report Parameter window should pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
SR: Investigate and fix the issue causing the Report Parameter window not to pop up when previewing a report with parameters.
